@gbraad it's a view panel, so the main UI has a set of can dialogs and flow but you can customize them to add additional Control elements so could be a checkbox.

(e.g. see https://github.com/GNOME/msitools/blob/master/data/ext/ui/WelcomeEulaDlg.wxs)

Here is an example of customizing: http://www.dizzymonkeydesign.com/blog/misc/adding-and-customizing-dlgs-in-wix-3/
